title: Glenn Miller Orchestra swinging into Winnipeg
text:
Glenn Miller Orchestra swinging into Winnipeg 
WINNIPEG SUN Tuesday, October 13, 2015 04:26 PM CDT | Updated: Tuesday, October 13, 2015 04:31 PM CDT 
The Glenn Miller Orchestra is bringing some of their trademark swing to The Burt. 
The legendary New York-based orchestra will play the Burton Cummings Theatre on March 2. The orchestra, founded 75 years ago, features 20 musicians and singers playing the legendary swing era bandleaderâ€™s most famous songs. 
Tickets for the two-hour greatest hits show, now led under the direction of Nick Hilsher, range from $53-$65, plus taxes and fees, and are on sale via Ticketmaster.
